Episodes.Title: Aang
Episodes.Writer: Albert Kim, Michael Dante DiMartino, Bryan Konietzko
Episodes.Plot: An Airbender comes to grips with his new reality as war erupts. A century later, a pair of Water Tribe siblings make a discovery that changes everything.

Episodes.Title: Warriors
Episodes.Writer: Joshua Hale Fialkov, Albert Kim, Bryan Konietzko
Episodes.Plot: Aang, Katara and Sokka arrive at a small island, home to elite warriors named after Avatar Kyoshi. The Fire Nation gets wind of the Avatar's whereabouts.

Episodes.Title: Omashu
Episodes.Writer: Christine Boylan, Albert Kim, Bryan Konietzko
Episodes.Plot: News of a traitor puts the trio at odds in Omashu, where a mechanist and rebels with a charming leader muddle their plans to protect the Earth Kingdom.

Episodes.Title: Into the Dark
Episodes.Writer: Keely MacDonald, Albert Kim, Bryan Konietzko
Episodes.Plot: In captivity, Aang meets a king with a taste for games. To find their friend, the siblings must navigate a dark tunnel - and put their differences aside.

Episodes.Title: Spirited Away
Episodes.Writer: Gabriel Llanas, Albert Kim, Bryan Konietzko
Episodes.Plot: When the group lands in the spirit world for a rescue mission, they come face to face with dangerous threats, painful memories and a mysterious entity.

Episodes.Title: Masks
Episodes.Writer: Emily Kim, Hunter Ries, Bryan Konietzko
Episodes.Plot: A desperate Aang visits Avatar Roku for help on his journey as the Fire Nation closes in on him. At the fortress, a masked intruder breaks Aang out.

Episodes.Title: The North
Episodes.Writer: Audrey Wong Kennedy, Albert Kim, Bryan Konietzko
Episodes.Plot: As an attack on the Northern Water Tribe looms, Katara challenges a master Waterbender, Sokka meets a princess and Aang takes Kuruk's words to heart.

Episodes.Title: Legends
Episodes.Writer: Albert Kim, Bryan Konietzko, Michael Dante DiMartino
Episodes.Plot: Zhao leads the Fire Nation into the North with a bold plan to weaken the Water Tribe. When the battle takes a dark turn, Aang enters a powerful state.
